<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-1769] parse of assert fails when newline between &apos;test&apos; and &apos;message&apos;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-1769</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>
&lt;p&gt;assert statements crashes the parser if a line break appears between the test and the message. i.e:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;assert test :&lt;br/&gt;
    &quot;message&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;see attached test case and stack trace.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
