                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14463749" author="aalmiray" created="Fri, 30 Nov 2007 00:51:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Java does allow the message to be written in the following line, the question is should Groovy too?&lt;br/&gt;
If the answer is no, this should be closed and a New Feature should be opened targeting a future release.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14463853" author="bpsm" created="Fri, 30 Nov 2007 04:00:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Agreed. Besides, there&apos;s a cute work-around:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;assert (test&lt;br/&gt;
       ): &quot;message&quot;;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Somehow the presence of a frowning &quot;smiley&quot; is fitting for a failed assertion.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14479335" author="genie" created="Sat, 4 Sep 2010 11:59:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I see it&apos;s an old issue not fixed yet. Do you have any plans about it?&lt;br/&gt;
I would also &lt;b&gt;love&lt;/b&gt; to simply write&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; test :
       message
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14479315" author="genie" created="Sat, 4 Sep 2010 12:01:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://groovy.329449.n5.nabble.com/assert-message-can-t-start-on-new-line-following-test-td340894.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://groovy.329449.n5.nabble.com/assert-message-can-t-start-on-new-line-following-test-td340894.html&lt;/a&gt; provides the following workarounds, though&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;: \ 
       &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;message&quot;&lt;/span&gt; 

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;, \ 
       &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;message&quot;&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I guess it can be good enough&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
